# This folder will contain the following artifacts after training:
#
#   training_checkpoints/
#   ├── checkpoint                          ← Tracks the latest checkpoint
#   ├── ckpt-1.index
#   ├── ckpt-1.data-00000-of-00001          ← Checkpoint saved at epoch 5
#   ├── ckpt-2.index
#   └── ckpt-2.data-00000-of-00001          ← Checkpoint saved at epoch 10
#
#   restored_output.jpg                     ← Output from inference.py
#
# Checkpoints are saved every 5 epochs (configurable in train.py).
# inference.py loads the latest checkpoint automatically.
#
# Run:  python src/GANs/train.py      to generate checkpoints
#       python src/GANs/inference.py  to generate restored_output.jpg
